To normalize an audio file in [[Digital Performer]] first you need to select the file in either the tracks window, sequence editor or soundbites window. Then go to '''Audio/Edit In Waveform Editor'''. Then select the area you want to normalize or '''Command A''' to select the entire file. Then go to '''Audio/Normalize'''

